{"title":"Cinderella_1차","lang":"arabic","lang_option":"2","device":"dotpad320","audioPath":"","items":[{"page":1,"title":"Cinderella_작업","graphic":{"name":"1.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"1.txt","data":"38200914193B1107070138000000000000000000","plain":"Cinderella"},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":56,"title":"Cinderella_작업","graphic":{"name":"2.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"2.txt","data":"3820151D09110200102E00070A272B00010000000E3A11111E001E110D0F3B2B001B0A1707001831101D003400200914193B11070701323800000000","plain":"Once, there lived a sweet tempered girl whose name was Cinderella."},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":55,"title":"Cinderella_작업","graphic":{"name":"3.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"3.txt","data":"382014002E0009221E3B000A0E00000000000000200914193B11070701003E00133B0013010A17000317010A192B001E15001015000E0A191102002F01000E0F1C05072C00111611091E000A0E00000019110F0A091E2B0001032700133B001302193238","plain":"In the center is Cinderella with her hair braided to one side, and a sparkling effect is depicted above her head."},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":54,"title":"","graphic":{"name":"","data":""},"text":{"name":"","data":"","plain":""},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":53,"title":"Cinderella_1차","graphic":{"name":"5.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"5.txt","data":"","plain":""},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":52,"title":"Cinderella_1차","graphic":{"name":"6.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"6.txt","data":"38202E00131517170A19000E0A0C3B0E000000000715272B001E150003150E0E0000000000000000200914193B110707013200202E000B0C000000000E19123800000000000000000000000000000000","plain":"The horrid sisters loved to boss Cinderella. The first said:"},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":51,"title":"Cinderella_작업","graphic":{"name":"7.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"7.txt","data":"38200914193B0E1600202D2034300E003D1700001A1503001E15000907021D002E000000000000000B0A17110F070109113200201E2034300E00313D3D2034171100090107072B00200914193B0E1600201B111E002D2618343800000000000000000000","plain":"“Cinders! It’s your job to clean the fireplace. That’s why you’re called Cinders! Get it?”"},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":50,"title":"Cinderella_1차","graphic":{"name":"8.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"8.txt","data":"3820151D002E0007110B1E000A0E000000000000200914193B1107070100131507192C0001000000031715150D001400101500132F02002F00151D002E001017000A0E0001000B0A17110F07010911003E000129110E0017110D01142C32380000000000","plain":"On the left is Cinderella holding a broom in one hand, and on the right is a fireplace with ashes remaining."},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":49,"title":"Cinderella_1차","graphic":{"name":"9.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"9.txt","data":"38202F00060B002911003813000B140A292B00000E3A11110F2C002E001B17011E1102002E0000000E1109151D19000E0A0C3B000E19023800000000","plain":"And before she had finished sweeping the grate, the second sister said,"},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":48,"title":"Cinderella_1차","graphic":{"name":"10.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"10.txt","data":"38200914193B0E16002019151D2034301E00000019013A190711320020070A231E00250F002E00000B0A1711002F000D010511000D1100010013151E030139003E000E3A11111E000E0D1107072C0000092F07110E161834380000000000000000000000","plain":"“Cinders! Don’t dawdle. Light up the fire and make me a hot bath with sweet smelling candles!”"},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":47,"title":"Cinderella_1차","graphic":{"name":"11.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"11.txt","data":"38200914193B11070701040E0013021E2C00250F2E000301393A011E3B3238000000000000000000","plain":"Cinderella's heating up the bathwater."},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":46,"title":"Cinderella_1차","graphic":{"name":"12.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"12.txt","data":"38202F003500291100340013021E2C002E00000003013902002E00131517170A1900100D000E1902200914193B0E160020313D00130127222034301E3D00031122001E15002E000D1C05111E000000003D111E2618343800000000000000000000000000","plain":"And as she was heating the bath, the horrid mother said, “Cinders! Why haven’t you been to the market yet?”"},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":45,"title":"Cinderella_1차","graphic":{"name":"13.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"13.txt","data":"","plain":""},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":44,"title":"Cinderella_1차","graphic":{"name":"14.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"14.txt","data":"38200914193B1107070100340017251D00370B00133B000B11111E000107070010190200000000000907021D2C02001E0A193D2C02002F000725362C0C250B0B001C2819323800000000000000000000","plain":"Cinderella was run off her feet all day, cleaning, tidying, and lugging stuff around."},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":43,"title":"","graphic":{"name":"","data":""},"text":{"name":"","data":"382014003A141E3B02002E00103D0000000000000701190A110E00360014270A1E2B001E15002E002017153D01070020030107073200203F0001000031150711000D151D39002E3D001E170A2B00151D1E0116111E010003010707001B2A1D0E020000000B170A07073D000F111E1E0A0915011E0E02002F0C17010F0F3D002915110E323800000000000000","plain":"In winter, the young ladies were invited to the Royal Ball. For a whole month they tried on taffeta ball gowns, frilly petticoats, and strappy shoes. \n"},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":42,"title":"Cinderella_1차","graphic":{"name":"16.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"16.txt","data":"38202D003400200914193B1107070102003700000933170E1102003115001311070F2B002E0D00142F0033003700382E00170A21000000000000000009150C250D110E02002F003115000F17110E0E2B2F000B1507192B0010113D392C320020133B00002A1D000907152E0E0036000000000000000000000F1701091E0A090107073D0017011B0E32380000","plain":"It was Cinderella, of course, who helped them in and out of their rich costumes, and who pressed and folded everything. Her own clothes were practically rags."},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":41,"title":"Cinderella_1차","graphic":{"name":"17.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"17.txt","data":"38200914193B11070701040E002017011B0E3800","plain":"Cinderella's Rags"},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":40,"title":"Cinderella_1차","graphic":{"name":"18.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"18.txt","data":"38202E00030A1B001D0A231E0009010D11002F000F15151700200914193B1107070100340000000007110B1E00011E0013150D1102000E0A1E1E2C000107101500033D002E00000000000000000000000B0A17110F070109113238000000000000000000","plain":"The big night came and poor Cinderella was left at home, sitting alone by the fireplace."},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":39,"title":"","graphic":{"name":"","data":""},"text":{"name":"","data":"382001000D330E110009010D1100250F001E1500133B002F000E1902002019111C020019111C020019151D2034301E000B17111E32002001001B19000B010A173D000A0E00331E0E0A191102002F00002911000E013D0E001E003D0029001B001E15002E0301070732183438000000000000000000000000","plain":"A mouse came up to her and said, “Dear, dear, don’t fret. A good fairy is outside, and she says that you shall go to the ball.”"},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":38,"title":"Cinderella_1차","graphic":{"name":"20.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"20.txt","data":"38200914193B11070701000E0A1E1E2C000000000107101500033D002E000B0A17110F0701091138","plain":"Cinderella sitting alone by the fireplace"},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":37,"title":"Cinderella_1차","graphic":{"name":"21.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"21.txt","data":"38200914193B11070701040E0015273B00102E00151D002E0007110B1E02002F00010007070000000D330E11000A0E001017001D112D1E001E150000133B3200202E000D330E11000A0E00071515052C011E00200914193B11070701002F000E11110D0E1E1500060021011E1E2C003E00133B3238000000","plain":"Cinderella's over there on the left, and a little mouse is right next to her. The mouse is looking at Cinderella and seems to be chatting with her."},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":36,"title":"Cinderella_1차","graphic":{"name":"22.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"22.txt","data":"38200914193B110707010017011D0033001E15002E000933171E3D1C19001031002E001B190000000B010A173D001E150719002E00103D00000000001B0A170732380000000000000000000000000000","plain":"Cinderella ran out to the courtyard where the good fairy told the young girl."},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":35,"title":"Cinderella_1차","graphic":{"name":"23.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"23.txt","data":"","plain":""},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":34,"title":"Cinderella_1차","graphic":{"name":"24.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"24.txt","data":"38202E000B010A173D003E002E000D011B0A09003A2F000A0E000B0715011E2C00151D002E00000007110B1E0200310A071100200914193B11070701131507192C000100031715150D000A0E00151D002E00101732380000000000000000000000000000","plain":"The fairy with the magic wand is floating on the left, while Cinderella holding a broom is on the right."},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":33,"title":"Cinderella_1차","graphic":{"name":"25.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"25.txt","data":"382001001B150719220009150121001E15150500133B001E15002E000F010701091102002F00151D2E003A013D0029110021011D1B2B00141E1500010302251E0A3007001B2A1D323800000000000000","plain":"A golden coach took her to the palace, and on the way she changed into a beautiful gown. "},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":26,"title":"Cinderella_1차","graphic":{"name":"26.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"26.txt","data":"3820102E001C11000E0F1C05072C000000000000111611091E0E001C281902002F0014002E0000000D0A191907110200102E000A0E000100000000001B15071922000F250D0F05140000000000000000091C170A011B1132380000000000000000000000","plain":"There are sparkling effects around, and in the middle, there is a golden pumpkin carriage."},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":31,"title":"Cinderella_1차","graphic":{"name":"27.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"27.txt","data":"3820312200291100221E3B2B002E000000000000030107071715150D020001070700113D110E0036182500133B020014090725192C00183900370000133B000E0A0C3B0E00311500190A19001D000000171109151B1D0A0E1100133B3238000000000000","plain":"When she entered the ballroom, all eyes were upon her, including those of her sisters who did not recognise her. \n"},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":30,"title":"Cinderella_1차","graphic":{"name":"28.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"28.txt","data":"38202E000F1714091100010E052B002E001D113A1C170A270107001E150019281102001D00000000151D091102000300011B002F00011B320020060B2E001127222C00340033020013110038130000000B0107072200140007152711003E002E000000000D3D0C3B0A330E00103D000601251E3D32380000","plain":"The prince asked the new arrival to dance, not once, but again and again. Before the evening was out, he had fallen in love with the mysterious young beauty. "},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":29,"title":"Cinderella_1차","graphic":{"name":"29.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"29.txt","data":"38202E000F17140911003E00010009172A1D0000151D002E0007110B1E0013010E0000000000000013111C1E2429010F2B00113D110E3200202F0000151D002E001017000A0E002E000302251E0A30071E17011D0E3F0D2B00200914193B110707013238","plain":"The prince with a crown on the left has heart-shaped eyes. And on the right is the beautiful transformed Cinderella."},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":28,"title":"Cinderella_1차","graphic":{"name":"30.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"30.txt","data":"382013110034000103001E1500010E05003F0000133B00132F0014000D1C170A011B11003122002E090715090500061B011D001E15000C170A0511001E3A110727113238000000000000000000000000","plain":"He was about to ask for her hand in marriage when the clock began to strike twelve.\n"},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":27,"title":"Cinderella_1차","graphic":{"name":"31.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"31.txt","data":"38202E000302251E0A300702000317010A192B000F17370A0711003700200914193B1107070100000A0E00151D002E0007110B1E02002F002E0000000907150905000F15141E2C001E150000000000000D0A191D0A231E000A0E00151D002E0010173238","plain":"The beautiful, braided profile of Cinderella is on the left, and the clock pointing to midnight is on the right."},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":26,"title":"Cinderella_1차","graphic":{"name":"32.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"32.txt","data":"382015131600203D000D0C00112D09250E1100000D1116183400112D0907010A0D2B000000000000200914193B11070701002F0029110017011D003F2E00191515173238000000000000000000000000","plain":"“Oh! You must excuse me!” exclaimed Cinderella and she ran for the door. \n"},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":25,"title":"Cinderella_1차","graphic":{"name":"33.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"33.txt","data":"382035002911001901292B00192A1D002E0000000C110F0E02001015003700133B0019011D092C000E070A0F0F3B0E000B110707000B00133B0000000B15151E002F002911003813001E150013150F001E15002E00091501213218263800000000000000","plain":"As she dashed down the steps, one of her dancing slippers fell from her foot and she had to hop to the coach.\""},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":34,"title":"Cinderella_1차","graphic":{"name":"34.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"34.txt","data":"38200914193B110707010007110B1E00061300001015003700133B001B07010E0E000000000000000E070A0F0F3B0E32380000000000000000000000","plain":"Cinderella left behind one of her glass slippers."},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":23,"title":"Cinderella_1차","graphic":{"name":"35.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"35.txt","data":"382014002E000D15171D2C02002E000000000000200F17140911000B2819002E0007150C000000000E070A0F0F3B002F001517193B2B0026000000000E3B27011D1E0E001E15001E010511002D00250F2F00192A1D002E00072F00251D1E0A07002E3D00320915273B2B002E000B15151E001E0000000000112D01091E073D000B0A1E1E2B002D3238000000","plain":"In the morning, the Prince found the lost slipper and ordered his servants to take it up and down the land until they discovered the foot that exactly fitted it."},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":22,"title":"Cinderella_1차","graphic":{"name":"36.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"36.txt","data":"38202E00010F0F111C28110037000000000000000E3B27011D1E0E001B152C001C2819001100000013330E1132380000000000000000000000000000","plain":"The appearance of servants going around every house."},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":21,"title":"Cinderella_1차","graphic":{"name":"36.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"36.txt","data":"38203122002E00200F171409112034300E0000000E3B27011D1E0E0009010D11001E15002E00000013330E1100103100200914193B11070701000000070A272B0200133B00131517170A1900000000000E0A0C3B0E00360011011B3B001E15001E173D00151D002E000E070A0F0F3B323800000000000000","plain":"When the Prince’s servants came to the house where Cinderella lived, her horrid sisters were eager to try on the slipper."},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":20,"title":"Cinderella_1차","graphic":{"name":"38.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"38.txt","data":"38202E000E0A0C3B000A0E00151D002E0000000007110B1E02002F002E00291511003E00011D000030202D001917013A1D00151D002D000A0E00151D2E00101732380000000000000000000000000000","plain":"The sister is on the left, and the shoe with an X drawn on it is on the right."},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":19,"title":"Cinderella_1차","graphic":{"name":"38.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"38.txt","data":"38202D000B0A1E0E000D110000000000000000000F3B0B11091E073D021834000E19002E000B0C0203002911000919001D002915271100133B00000013020700140E0A19113218263800000000000000","plain":"“It fits me perfectly,” said the first, but she could not shove her heal inside.\""},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":18,"title":"","graphic":{"name":"","data":""},"text":{"name":"","data":"38203D00090009010707000D110200203D1700002017153D01070020130A23300E203400060900000D3D000B15151E000B0A1E0E000000000000000003111E1E3B021834000E19002E000000000000000E1109151D193238000000000000000000000000","plain":"“You can call me, ‘Your Royal Highness’ because my foot fits better,” said the second. "},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":17,"title":"Cinderella_1차","graphic":{"name":"41.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"41.txt","data":"382003002D0034000907111C001E00133B0000000B15151E0034001127220007110E0E00010307111E15000E070A0F00141E15002E000000000000000E070A0F0F3B3218263800000000000000000000","plain":"But it was clear that her foot was even less able to slip into the slipper.\""},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":16,"title":"Cinderella_1차","graphic":{"name":"42.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"42.txt","data":"38201E173D2C001E15000E1F2511113511003D170B15151E00141E150001001B07010E0E000000000E070A0F0F3B3238000000000000000000000000","plain":"Trying to squeeze your foot into a glass slipper."},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":15,"title":"Cinderella_1차","graphic":{"name":"41.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"41.txt","data":"38202E0017153D0107000E3B27011D1E00000000071515052B00250F002F000E013A000000000000200914193B11070701000E0A1E1E2C00033D002E0B0A17110F07010911001E002911003813000000031122000907021D2C3238000000000000000000","plain":"The royal servant looked up and saw Cinderella sitting by the fireplace that she had been cleaning. "},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":14,"title":"Cinderella_1차","graphic":{"name":"42.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"42.txt","data":"3820102E0034000100030A1E0037000E15151E00151D00133B001D150E1102002F002D000D011911133B000B01091100010707002E000D0000000000211C0D2C3200201311000E191238000000000000","plain":"There was a bit of soot on her nose, and it made her face all the more charming. He said:"},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":13,"title":"Cinderella_1차","graphic":{"name":"45.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"45.txt","data":"38203A19003D00091C11001E15001E173D00151D2E0029151102000D0A0E0E2618340020313D000003152E17003E00133B26002029112034300E001A2E000D010A19021834000E19002E000000000000131517170A19000E0A0C3B0E2034000000000000100D321826380000000000000000000000000000","plain":"“Would you care to try on the shoe, miss?”\n“Why bother with her? She’s just the maid,” said the horrid sisters’ mother.\"\n"},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":12,"title":"Cinderella_1차","graphic":{"name":"46.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"46.txt","data":"38202E000B0109110037002E000C110F100D002F2E000E0A071333111E1E11003700000000000000200914193B110707013238000000000000000000","plain":"The face of the stepmother and the silhouette of Cinderella."},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":11,"title":"Cinderella_1차","graphic":{"name":"44.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"44.txt","data":"38200A003A190007001E15001E173D020000000039011D05003D021834000E190000000000000000200914193B11070701320020133B000B15151E000E070A0F0F2B00140000000000000000000000000F3B0B11091E073D321826380000000000000000","plain":"“I would like to try, thank you,” said Cinderella. Her foot slipped in perfectly.\""},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":10,"title":"Cinderella_1차","graphic":{"name":"45.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"45.txt","data":"38203115003A19001300391033002D26002033171F25110C000A0E0009150D0F07111E110218340019090719002E0017153D010700000000000000000E3B27011D1E3218263800000000000000000000","plain":"“Who would have thought it? Our quest is complete,” declared the royal servant.\""},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":9,"title":"Cinderella_1차","graphic":{"name":"46.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"46.txt","data":"382031011E26183400112D0907010A0D2B002E00100D3200203D20342711001B151E001E15000600050A19192C161834380000000000000000000000","plain":"“What?” exclaimed the mother. “You’ve got to be kidding!”"},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":8,"title":"Cinderella_1차","graphic":{"name":"50.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"50.txt","data":"38203D000A190A151E02003D20342711001B151E2E003A17301B001B0A17070218340000000000000F17151E110C2B002E00131517170A19000000000E0A0C3B0E321826380000000000000000000000","plain":"“You idiot, you’ve got the wrong girl,” protested the horrid sisters.\""},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":7,"title":"Cinderella_1차","graphic":{"name":"51.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"51.txt","data":"38202E000E3B27011D1E0E002F002E00000000000C110F100D003115001C1100011E001519190E003E0011012100152E173238000000000000000000","plain":"The servants and the stepmother who are at odds with each other."},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":6,"title":"Cinderella_1차","graphic":{"name":"48.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"48.txt","data":"382003002E000E3B27011D1E0034000107170000090107072C003F002E00091501210D011D001E151E01051100200914193B11070701001E15002E000F010701091102001917110E0E2B001400133B0017011B0E02380000000000000000000000000000","plain":"But the servant was already calling for the coachman to take Cinderella to the palace, dressed in her rags, "},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":5,"title":"","graphic":{"name":"","data":""},"text":{"name":"","data":"38112D01091E073D0035002911003A010E02002F3A111C2C00133B001D15170D0107002915110000151D001015000B15151E02002F00133B0000000019011D092C000E070A0F0F3B00151D002E000000152E173238000000000000000000000000000000","plain":"exactly as she was, and wearing her normal shoe on one foot, and her dancing slipper on the other."},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":4,"title":"Cinderella_1차","graphic":{"name":"50.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"50.txt","data":"38203500200914193B110707010007110B1E002E13330E1102002E00100D0037002E000000000000131517170A19001B0A17070E0009170A2B003302201B1900170A191928111600203A112034271100381300220037003D170021111105161834380000","plain":"As Cinderella left the house, the mother of the horrid girls cried out, “Good riddance! We’ve had enough of your cheek!”"},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":3,"title":"Cinderella_1차","graphic":{"name":"55.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"55.txt","data":"38200300200914193B1107070100051D113A001E2911003813000B2819001E1725110007152711022F002E0027001D112D1E00101902002911002F002E000F1714091